That skin though. Glammed the beautiful @siennamaegomez on @maybelline's YouTube. Swipe-up in my stories to check it out #MaybellinePartner #makeupbyariel

node.text:
Omgg😱😫😱😭😭 we just launched! I’m crying!! Sales are live Now! you can shop at Morphe.com (link in bio) and In store at @morphebrushes and online @ultabeauty, @sephoracanada @meccabeauty !!! Make sure to use code “Ariel “ at check out to save some money on your purchase!! This such a surreal moment and I cannot believe it’s happening!! Thank you to everyone for your support and I hope you guys enjoy these brush sets as much as I have!

 All of my brushes are tested and perfected by me and come in two luxurious sets: The SIGNATURE LOOK 12-piece face & eye brush set ($98) and The SIGNATURE EYES 8-piece eye brush set ($48us).
 

Shop the collection NOW on morphe.com + Morphe stores, @meccabeauty, @ultabeauty (online), @sephoacanada (online)

node.text: This is a video you don’t want to miss out on!! I filmed with @patrickstarrr pretty much my entire glam process👀! 😱 I did this a thank you to all of you guys for all the support on my Collab with @morphebrushes and we kind of explain the use of each brush as I use them and how I like to use them! 😍 go check it out on his YouTube channel and let me know if you like it! Maybe I’ll do more on my own YouTube channel🙈🙊🙊
